(36, 'Lotus Herbals', 'White Glow Skin Whitening and Brightening SPF-25 Hand and Body Lotion, 300ml\r\nQuantity: 300ml; Item Form: Cream \r\nFocus on dry or stressed areas such as elbows, heels, and knees \r\nCan be used any time your skin is feeling particularly parched and dry \r\nLightens: It lightens the skin tone by reducing uneven pigmentation \r\nSkin Type: All Skin Types \r\nTarget Audience: Unisex \r\nPackage Contents: 1 Hand And Body Lotion \r\nCountry of Origin: India ', 201, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(37, 'Vaseline', 'Vaseline Intensive Care Deep Moisture Body Lotion, 400 ml\r\nVaseline Deep Moisture Body Lotion is India’s No.1 Best-Selling Body Lotion \r\nIt’s double-action formula contains Glycerin which helps to replenish the lost moisture of your skin and Vaseline Jelly which is known to lock in the moisture in your skin \r\nPenetrates 5 layers^ deep into your skin and moisturises for all day soft, smooth skin \r\nIt is fast absorbing for a non-greasy feel and moisturises from the very first application \r\nDaily body lotion best for: dry skin, rough skin \r\nSmart pump quick-lock technology unlocks and locks with no mess', 201, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(38, 'Parachute ', 'Parachute Advansed Body Lotion Deep Nourish, 400 ml\r\nParachute Advance Body Lotion has unique Cocolipid Formula which goes 10 layers deep** in the skin to boost your natural glow \r\nNon-sticky fast absorbing formula with unique moisture lock technology that prevents moisture loss \r\nEnriched with Coconut Milk & 100% Natural moisturizing properties, nourishes the skin making it soft and supple all day long! \r\nIdeal for extra dry skin. For Men \r\nContains 100% natural moisturizers* that nourish from deep within. Helps retain skin\'s natural moisture. And its fragrance…. You\'d love it !! \r\nApply the Parachute Advansed Deep Nourish Body Lotion generously all over your body after a bath or shower or before you go for a sweet night sleep and massage in circular motions, paying special attention to any dry areas. \r\n', 165, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(39, 'Himalaya Herbals', 'Cocoa Butter Intensive Body Lotion, 400ml \r\nQuantity: 400ml; Item Form: Lotion \r\nOur moisturizer is enriched with the goodness of Cocoa Butter and Wheat Germ Oil, which replenish the lost moisture in dry skin \r\nNaturally derived ingredients restore skin\'s elasticity, leaving it softer and more toned than before \r\nSkin Type: Dry Skin \r\nUsage: Apply Cocoa Butter Intensive Body Lotion gently all over the body, with special attention to severely dry areas, slowly massaging it in \r\nTarget Audience: Men & Women \r\nPackage Contents: 1 Body Lotion.The Product appearance may differ from the actual image on the website due to packaging changes \r\nCountry of Origin: India\r\n', 201, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(40, 'Mamaearth', 'Vitamin C Body Lotion with Vitamin C & Honey for Radiant Skin – 400 ml \r\nDEEP HYDRATION: Vitamin C promotes even complexion and has anti-aging benefits. Honey soothes, hydrates, and reduces dullness. Daily use of the body lotion restores the skin’s suppleness. \r\nNON-GREASY FORMULA: Mamaearth Vitamin C Body Lotion is light, absorbs quickly into the skin, and gets to work immediately, giving the skin the hydration it craves. \r\nMADE WITH NATURAL INGREDIENTS: The unique body lotion prevents photodamage thanks to Vitamin C. Natural ingredients like Honey, Shea Butter, and Olive Oil are excellent for skin healing and balancing the skin’s pH. \r\nSUITABLE FOR ALL SKIN TYPES: This body lotion is dermatologically tested & is suitable for all skin types.', 378, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(41, 'Enchanteur', 'Romantic Perfumed Body Lotion\r\n250ml, with Aloe Vera & Olive Butter for Satin Smooth Skin\r\nMoisture silk aloevera and olive butter \r\nFor beautifully soft, silky smooth skin ', 165, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
(42, 'Yardley', 'London English Lavender Moisturising Hand & Body Lotion, 350ml(Pack of 2) \r\nInfused with \"flower power\" of natural floral extracts \r\nContains the goodness of 10,000 active floral cells in every 100 ml for beautifully soft and glowing skin \r\nWith over 240 years\' expertise, yardley london selects only the finest ingredients for its products ', 319, '1', '1', '2021-06-23', 1),
