(191, 'Alexvyan Silicone Gel Orthotic Toe and Finger Separator ', 'Relax those tense toes into a gentle stretch\r\nSpecial for manicure pedicure and nail art\r\nCan help many feet related problems including: hammertoes, bunions, plantar fasciitis, crossed toes, poor circulation and corns\r\nMaterial: silicone, colour: blue', 289, '1', '3', '2021-06-26', 1),
