(193, 'Himalaya baby powder', 'Description\r\nHimalaya\'S Baby Powder Is Formulated With Herbal Ingredients Which Helps Keeps Baby\'S Skin Cool And Comfortable.<br>\r\nSuperior powder infused with the power of herbs and zinc oxide<br>\r\nInstructions Included<br>\r\nYashad bhasma (zinc oxide) protects and prevents skin from rashes and infections<br>\r\nOlive oil and almond oil: vitamin e nourishes the skin and keeps skin soft and moisturized<br>\r\nSoft and coarse talc, which does not block the skin pores like other talcs<br>\r\nKhus grass: keeps skin cool and fresh. Organic : Yes<br>\r\nPACKER: The Himalaya Drug Company,Tumkur Road, Makali, Bangalore - 562162; IMPORTER: The Himalaya Drug Company,Tumkur Road, Makali, Bangalore - 562162<br>\r\nFree from parabens, phthalates and synthetic colors, the usual factors for rashes and allergies\r\n', 226, '7', '32', '2021-06-26', 1),
(194, 'Himalaya Baby Cream, 200ml', 'Description\r\nHimalaya Baby Cream is specially formulated to protect your little one\'s chapped cheeks, \'crawler\'s knee\', tender nose, and rubbed elbows. Our Baby Cream has soothing effect on baby\'s skin. The key ingredients work to moisturize along with preserving the natural softness of your baby\'s skin.<br>\r\nSoft cream infused with the power of herbs. Organic : Yes. Dermatologist Tested : Yes<br>\r\nOlive Oil: Vitamin E nourishes and keeps your baby’s skin moisturized<br>\r\nCountry Mallow (Bala): Protects the baby’s skin<br>\r\nLicorice: Soothes and makes the skin soft & supple<br>\r\nFree from Parabens, Mineral Oil & Synthetic Colors, the usual factors for rashes & allergies<br>\r\nSpecially formulated for tender areas such as cheeks, nose, elbows, and knees<br>\r\nMoisturizes and preserves natural softness of your baby’s skin<br>\r\nPACKER: The Himalaya Drug Company,Tumkur Road, Makali, Bangalore - 562162; IMPORTER: The Himalaya Drug Company,Tumkur Road, Makali, Bangalore - 562162', 185, '7', '32', '2021-06-26', 1),
