(225, 'L\'Oreal Paris Extraordinary Oil', ' Hair Serum for Women and Men, 100 ml \r\nTHE L\'OREAL PARIS SERUM DEEP NOURISHMENT - L\'Oral Paris Extraordinary Oil Hair Serum gives luscious, lightweight hair oil serum for dry hair, lifeless hair - Apply and experience transformation from the 1st use!\r\nWITH 6 OIL-COMPLEX FOR DAMAGED HAIR - Blend of 6 rare flower oils and oils like sunflower oil, coconut oil and soyabean oil with other botanical extracts, that provides hydration for hair and seals the hair cuticle - One of the best hair serums for dry and frizzy hair!\r\nVERSATILE USE- This hair product can be used in the following ways! - Before Shampoo - To provide hair nourishment and prep hair before washing - Before Hair Drying - To provide hair protection from heat & give smooth hair as it dries - Before Hair Styling - To smoothen out frizzy hair and give manageable hair from unruly hair strands - For Beautiful Hair - To give long-lasting freshness, lustrous & shiny hair - As Overnight Hair Treatment - To provide deep hair nourishment, for you to wake up with disciplined, manageable hair!\r\nHOW TO USE- Apply after shampoo and conditioner for instant shine & silky hair touch - Rub 3-4 precious drops between your palms to warm this anti-frizz hair serum. Apply evenly through the lengths and ends on wet or dry hair\r\nSuitable for normal hair, dry hair, dull hair, rough hair, frizzy hair & damaged hair', 399, '1', '4', '2021-06-28', 1),
