(293, 'Lenskart Junior For Kids Age 8-12 yrs | Bluecut & Antiglare Zero power | Sky Blue | Cat Eye Computer Eyeglasses | LKJ E10010CE', 'Care Instructions: Apply Aqualens Solution Spray and use selvyt cloth to clean the glasses.\r\nAbout Blu Lens Technology:- Featuring Blu Lens technology which helps in protecting your kid’s eyes by blocking the harmful blue light emitted by digital devices like smartphone and computer as well as filter the UV rays from the sun.\r\nFrame Material & Dimension:-Featuring premium sky blue spectacles from Lenskart. Made from a combination of TR90 which is flexible and lightweight and Stainless Steel which is durable and sturdy, making them perfect for the your kids’ active lifestyle | Frame Width:-124 mm | For Kids Age (8-12 yrs)\r\nLens Material:-Featuring Blue Cut lenses which are Anti Glare and Crack Resistant, offering UV400 protection and are hydrophobic& dust repellent.\r\nFrame Style:-Cateyes evoke effortless grace and style and give the kids an elegant and classy look.\r\nCare Instruction:- Eyeglasses help kids see clearly and in focus. It is important to clean and maintain them regularly. Just spray some Aqualens solution on your lenses and wipe them with a microfibre cloth to keep your lenses pristine.', 799, '4', '22', '2021-07-11', 1),
