(301, 'Bold Care Topical Spray for Men | Non-transferable | 20g (Pack of 1)', 'DIRECTIONS OF USE - Spray 1-4 times, rub it in a circular motion on the area, let it stay for 15 minutes.\r\nSAFE & NON TRANSFERABLE - The spray is safe with no side effects, and is also non-transferable keeping everyone\'s health and safety in mind.\r\nQUALITY ASSURANCE - Our products are doctor-backed and clinically-approved to ensure health and wellness for men.', 300, '9', '50', '2021-07-11', 1),
