(303, 'StBotanica Peach and Avocado Shower Gel (Moisturizing Body Wash With Pure Essential Oils), 300ml', 'Moisturizing shower gel that instantly turns your daily shower into a mini-spa experience\r\nCleanses skin without over-drying, brings peace to mind, makes you feel great, moisturizes and softens skin\r\nFree of parabens, soap, mineral oils and harmful chemical derivatives\r\nThis luxury shower gel, will leave your skin feeling refreshed and invigorated\r\nEnriched with pure essential oils', 322, '9', '49', '2021-07-11', 1),
