(305, 'Herb Island Berry Fusion Body Yoghurt & Mineral Oil, Silicones & Parabens Free;150gm', 'Lightweight formula that moisturises the skin without any greasy feeling.\r\nFast absorbing & gives immense hydration to the skin.\r\nFresh berry extracts & floral extracts soothe irritated skin, while shea butter & olive oil moisturises.\r\nFor All Skin Types. Sulphate, Paraben, Silicones, Mineral Oil & Petrolatum Free.\r\nThe sweet & citrusy scent of berries will not only leave your skin feel fresh, fruity and fragrant but will also hydrate and moisturise with the goodness of Shea Butter & Olive Oil. The superfruit juices will leave your skin glowing. This lightweight formula is best suited for summers.', 349, '9', '53', '2021-07-11', 1),
(306, 'BAENE: Cucumber and Aloe Body Yogurt (200 ml) | Cool Rejuvenating Moisturizer for All Skin Types', 'NATURAL MOISTURIZER AND COOLANT: BAENE Cucumber & Aloe Body Yogurt spreads easily on skin with a wonderful cooling sensation. Formulated to absorb, smoothen and soften the skin with rapidly absorbing and non-sticky texture. Adds moisture and gives healthy-looking, soft and supple skin.\r\nESSENTIAL EXTRACTS: The cucumber extracts is a perfect combination in the mousse to pamper your skin from all the harshness it faces due to the varying weather.\r\nNATURAL AND FRESH: Enriched with Cucumber extracts that keeps your skin hydrated. It contains Fresh cucumber & green tea scent with cooling sensation which helps you to Radiate and Glow.\r\nVEGAN CREAM - 100% VEGAN. Does NOT contain harmful chemicals such as Parabens, SLS, SLES and more\r\nSUITABILITY - Suitable for all skin types, can be used everyday.', 400, '9', '53', '2021-07-11', 1),
(307, 'L\'Oreal Paris Revitalift Crystal Micro-Essence, 22 ml', 'A brightening micro-essence - better than creams, moisturizers and face serums\r\nFor glowing and radiant skin\r\nFor all skin types, including oily and dry skin types\r\nContains Salicylic Acid that keeps skin Hydrated and Moisturized\r\nUse day and night after cleansing to get brighter, clearer skin', 213, '9', '53', '2021-07-11', 1),
