(490, 'Gopendra 11pcs/Set Fitness Resistance Bands - Workout Bands with Handles, Door Anchor, Ankle Straps, Training Tubes Practical Exercise Bands, Training Equipment for Arm Leg Training Gym Home Exercise', 'ANTI-SNAP PROMISE :– Our premium workout bands are made of the highest quality, using 100% Natural Latex from Malaysia with high elasticity and extra thick high-grade silicon that will not dry out, snap, or deform. Developed with you in mind, each tube band is double layered and carefully constructed to provide maximum resistance! Our team at Tribe Fitness has 10+ years of experience manufacturing silicon products and we fully stand behind the quality of our products!\r\nMULTI FUNCTIONAL :– The resistance Tube can be used to exercise all parts of muscles such as arms, chest, abdomen, glutes and legs, also good for Physical Therapy, Recovery or to increase Mobility.\r\nECO-FRIENDLY MATERIAL :– 100% Free of Latex, Highest Quality Rubber and Tpr Foam. We Pay More Attention to the Workmanship and Also the Raw Material. the Protective Double Layer End Sleeves Reduces Wear and Provides Longer Band Life.\r\nVERSATILE :– Resistance Bands Are Extremely Versatile, Great for p90x, Insanity, Cross Fit Training, Yoga, Pilates, Beach Body, Physical Therapy, Strengthening, Toning Upper and Lower Body. You Can Also Isolate and Target Glutes, Legs, Hips & Knees.\r\nCREATE YOUR IDEAL RESISTANCE BANDS SET :– Our Single Resistance Bands can be purchased in your ideal resistance level to create the ultimate exercise bands that is specifically tailored to your workouts or fitness routines. Whether you are a professional athlete looking to enhance your training, a beginner or an expert exercise enthusiast looking for a more effective workout, this versatile set will empower your training for faster and more effective results!', 999, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(491, 'SPORTAL Air Bike Fix Handle Exercise Cycle', 'Brand	SPORTAL\r\nColour	Black\r\nResistance Mechanism	Air\r\nMaterial	Alloy Steel\r\nAbout this item: Provides A Low Impact Workout & Strengthen Muscles: It provides a low impact workout at your home according to your convenience and helps in strengthening the muscles of your hands, legs and the whole lower body as well\r\nSportal Air Bike comes with dual option of stationary or moving handles for your convenience which means it can be used for full body cardio or only lower body cardio as well\r\nExercise Air Bike: Sportal Air bike is a portable, non- motorized, exercise cycle specially designed for home use. It helps in boosting your daily cardio routine\r\nPerformance Tracker & Speed Knob: The Sportal Air Bike comes with a Performance Tracker to track your progress in terms of distance, speed, time covered and a Manual Speed Knob to adjust the speed as per your requirement\r\nBrand	‎SPORTAL\r\nColor	‎Black\r\nIncluded Components	‎Instruction Manual, Cycle Frame, Air Bike Accessories, Screws & Key\r\nMaterial Type	‎Alloy Steel\r\nMeter	‎Speed, Time, Distance\r\nNumber of Items	‎1\r\nStyle	‎Exercise Cycle with Twister and Back Support\r\nManufacturer	‎SPORTAL\r\nCountry of Origin	‎India', 15000, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(492, 'RYLAN Double Spring Tummy Trimmer Pro Waist Trimmer Abs Exerciser Body Toner Fat Buster Home Gym Home Exercise Equipment Abdominal Exercise Equipment Leg Exerciser Tummy Trimmer for Men and Women', 'Tummy Trimmer & Hand Gripper in One: The ab exerciser targets specific muscles of your body to build your fitness. Rowing movements of this exerciser trims and tones your abdominal muscles and strengthens your arms, legs, hips and thighs. It burns extra calories, melts away your abdominal fat around your waist to give you a flat and firm stomach. The exerciser also functions as a hand gripper. Grip the inner handle and pull. It exercises your arms, wrists, fingers, forearms simultaneously\r\nHeavy Duty Steel Springs: Heavy duty carbon steel springs create resistance and builds your muscles. The long springs build resistance to build your upper and lower body muscles. The shorter hand gripper springs build resistance to develop hand, wrist and forearms.\r\nAdjustable to different fitness levels: The ab exerciser can be adjusted to varying fitness and resistance levels. The steel springs can be removed or added back to adjust the resistance\r\nPortable Fitness Equipment: The ab exerciser is portable fitness equipment that can be used in your home or gym comfortably. It comes fully assembled for immediate use. The steel springs can be removed easily and put back on the expander. It is beneficial for beginners and advanced users.\r\nBrand	‎Rylan\r\nColor	‎Multi\r\nSize	‎M\r\nManufacturer	‎harikrishnavilla\r\nCountry of Origin	‎India', 999, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(493, 'RYLAN Resistance Loop Bands Set for Squats, Stretching, Strength Training Exercises, Hips & Glutes Heavy Workouts for Men & Women (Carry Bag Included) Resistance Bands', 'RESISTANCE BANDS THAT ARE EASY TO USE : Made from 100% latex. Comes in 5 different resistance strength levels: X-Light, Light, Medium, Heavy and X-Heavy. They\'re suitable for beginner or a seasoned workout sportsman.\r\nTAKE YOUR WORKOUTS TO THE NEXT LEVEL: Whether you are a beginner or expert, resistance bands have a place in your home gym. Resistance bands work your muscles like weights do – your muscles contract to generate force to stabilize and control the desired\r\nEFFICIENT WORKOUT: Loop Resistance Bands increase the effectiveness of your exercises. Used for a range of workouts, from glute and hip activation, strength techniques to integrate seamlessly with every workout program such as Yoga, Pilates,etc.\r\nMULTIFUNCTIONAL: The resistance band set can be used to exercise all parts of muscles such as arms, chest, abdomen, glutes and legs, also good for Physical Therapy, Recovery or to increase Mobility.\r\nGREAT INVESTMENT FOR YOUR BODY: Even just spending 15-20 minutes per day with our resistance bands results in consistent progress!\r\nBrand	‎RYLAN\r\nColor	‎Multicolour\r\nIncluded Components	‎Exc\r\nStyle	‎Loop\r\nCountry of Origin	‎India', 1199, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(494, 'SKYFUN (LABEL) Pull Rope Fitness Equipment for Sit-up Bodybuilding Expander Abdomen Workout Arm Stretching Slimming Training Reducer', 'Style	Classic\r\nMaterial	Rubber\r\nBrand	SKYFUN (LABEL)\r\nTension Level	Free\r\nItem Weight	250 Grams\r\nAbout this item: The 2-tube fitness rope is made of foam, comfortable to hold and grip, non-toxic and safe, no harm to your body; The 2 drawstrings have nice tensile strength and elasticity, durable for you to use long time.\r\nFoot pedal band get rid of your spare tire in the easiest way. Once you own it, you can do sit-ups without effort by yourself, and carry out the plan to thin your waist.\r\nYou can use the elastic pull rope at home, gym, hotel room, office, or even outdoors.\r\nThis resistance bands set is small, lightweight and can be carried around. You can do exercise anywhere, such as home, gym, office, hotel, beach and travel, etc.\r\n1 Piece Adjustable Pull Rubber Rope Reducer Exercise Kit-Multi Color', 599, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(495, 'HNESS push up board for men & Women at home', 'Color Name: Pushup Board-H1\r\nBrand	HNESS\r\nMaterial	PLASTIC\r\nColour	Pushup Board-H1\r\nItem Dimensions LxWxH	50 x 70 x 30 Millimeters\r\nAbout this item\r\nPortable:- The new product adopts collapsible and portable design style; It will be not difficult to carry the push-up board to everywhere with the complimentary backpack\r\nProfessional Training Programs:- The complimentary Training Schedule List is a fitness program developed by professional fitness coaches for different levels of exercisers\r\nSilicone Anti-slip Handgrip:- Increased friction, reducing the possibility of slip, to do your workout more safty and powerful\r\n17 in 1:- Each side has 17 different ways to use holes. Through the combination of different holes on both sides, more training methods can be formed\r\nDouble Lock:- Utilizing Snap Fit joints and Heavy Duty Plug-ins, the handles are firmly attached to the Push-up Board allowing for a steady and secure workout', 599, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
(496, 'Stunner Fitness 3.0HP (6.0HP Peak) Multi-Functional Motorised Treadmill with Auto Inclination | Bluetooth | MP3 | Smart Phone App for Cardio Workout at Home (Free Installation Assistance)', '\r\nBrand	Stunner Fitness\r\nColour	Multi\r\nMaterial	Aluminium\r\nItem Dimensions LxWxH	170 x 78 x 35 Centimeters\r\nPower Source	Corded Electric\r\nAbout this item\r\nWarranty: Lifetime Frame Warranty, 3-Years Motor Warranty, and 1-Year Parts & Manufacturing Defects Warranty. Performance: Motorised treadmill with powerful DC Motor 3.0 HP Continuous Power and 6.0 HP Peak Power. Speed of 1.0-18km/H with select Hot keys . With Auto Inclination of 0-15 Level maximum gradient make the workout extremely effective, be it running, jogging or walking.\r\nFuturistic Console: Display with 7” inch LED Display -we have equipped the STX-365 treadmill with an integrated touch keys control pad, which enables reliable experience of touch screen.Keep an eye on Speed, Distance, Time, Calories and Heart Rate. With Select Hot Keys for Speed and Inclination. Interactive Training: To burn calories more effectively, we specially programmed 12 pre-installed training programs and 3 Preset Target based Modes to create a customized routine of exercises\r\nSemi Auto-Lubricating Function: The innovative Semi Auto-lubricating system makes maintenance of the STX-365 extremely practical. It provides an even distribution of the silicone frequent and annoying re-oiling is no longer necessary. Natural Running Experience: The large running surface (1360 x 520 mm) allows a training with the treadmill. Max. user weight is 140 kg.\r\nMobile App: The folding treadmill support Bluetooth smartphone Android & IOS App connect. App allows you to control treadmill, view and record sports data & share data in social media . Connect with treadmill and then set your personal training plan. Multi Functional: We have equipped this treadmill with Massager, Twister, Dumbbells & Sit-up Bar so that you use it for Multiple exercises.\r\nBrand	‎Stunner Fitness\r\nColor	‎Multi\r\nDisplay Size	‎7 Inches\r\nDisplay Type	‎LCD\r\nIncluded Components	‎Treadmill1\r\nMaterial Type	‎Aluminium\r\nHorsepower	‎6 Horsepower\r\nNumber of Items	‎1\r\nNumber Of Programs	‎12\r\nPower Source	‎Corded Electric\r\nSpeed Rating	‎T\r\nSport	‎Exercise & Fitness\r\nStyle	‎All-season\r\nManufacturer	‎Stunner fitness\r\nCountry of Origin	‎China', 136072, '8', '41', '2021-07-17', 1),
